stimulusHtml: What is the value of  end  after the code segment is executed?

features.html:
Consider the following code segment.

 

int start = 4; 
int end = 5; 
 
if (start < end) 
{ 
   if (end > 0) 
   { 
      start += 2; 
      end++; 
   } 
   else 
   { 
      end += 3; 
   } 
} 
 
if (start < end) 
{ 
   if (end == 0) 
   { 
      end += 2; 
      start++; 
   } 
   else 
   { 
      end += 4; 
   } 
}
